<section id="trgLang">
    <title>trgLang</title>
    
    <para>Target language - the code of the language, in which the <firstterm>Translated</firstterm> text is
        expressed.</para>
    <para><emphasis>Type:</emphasis><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?>
        string.<?oxy_custom_end?></para>
    
    <para><emphasis>Value description:</emphasis> A language code as described in <olink targetdoc="../xliff21.xml"
        targetptr="bcp47">[BCP 47]</olink>.</para>
    
    <para><emphasis>Default value:</emphasis> undefined.</para>
    
    <para><emphasis>Used in:</emphasis>
        <olink targetdoc="../elements/structural/xliff.xml" targetptr="xliff"
            ><code>jliff</code></olink>.</para>
</section>

